fields.job_title: Senior Manager, Business Banking, TD Bank Financial Group
fields.name: Irene Law
fields.description:
Irene Law is Senior Manager, Business Banking with TD Bank Financial Group. She has been involved with assisting businesses grow throughout her various roles in the bank. During this time, she has been a commercial lender to a variety of businesses from small, emerging companies to large multinational corporations.

Irene has written articles directed at small businesses on topics ranging from business plans to financing. In her current role, Irene is responsible for developing strategies to drive business banking growth at TD Canada Trust.

fields.name: Dave Olson
fields.description:
Dave Olson (@daveohoots) is the Community Marketing Director for social media dashboard maker HootSuite. Working in the Internet space since 1996, Dave was a partner at two successful Internet Service Providers plus worked with start-ups including ecommerce software, open source web development, and a green business directory.

Dave frequently presents at events, and appears in the media discussing technology, art, hockey and culture. A chronic documentarian from his earliest days, Dave creates visual art, writes essays and produces podcasts and led a ground-breaking project for social coverage of the Vancouver Olympics. After living and traveling worldwide, Dave now enjoys exploring his local North Vancouver mountains and forests.
